Place the following TTF files here, then run `npx react-native-asset`:

  DMSans-Regular.ttf
  DMSans-Medium.ttf
  DMSans-Bold.ttf
  Lora-Regular.ttf
  Lora-Bold.ttf

DM Sans:  https://fonts.google.com/specimen/DM+Sans
Lora:     https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Lora

The font family names referenced in code (src/lib/theme.ts) match the
PostScript names above. On iOS, confirm the names with Font Book if a glyph
renders in the system font instead of the bundled face.
